title: Teen with autism's story goes viral after touchdown run (Autism Speaks Inc)
text: ( Source : Autism Speaks Inc) An inspiration in his local community in Atlanta , Logan Pickett, an 18-year-old senior with autism from Heritage High School is receiving national attention for his performance both on and off the football field.
